    <description>
        <en>
<![CDATA[Use to quickly have the vehicle camera;
rotate 45-degrees left/right, look forwards/backwards or zoom in/out.


Decker_MMIV - fs-uk.com, forum.farming-simulator.com, modhoster.com]]>
        </en>
        <de>
<![CDATA[Schnelles wechseln der Fahrzeug-Kamera,
45 Grad-Drehung links/rechts, sehe nach vorne/hinten oder Zoome rein/raus


Decker_MMIV - fs-uk.com, forum.farming-simulator.com, modhoster.com]]>
        </de>
    <!-- http://translate.google.com - English to ... - Please PM me a better translation. -->
        <fr>
<![CDATA[Utilisez avoir rapidement la caméra du véhicule;
tourner de 45 degrés vers la gauche/droite, regardez avant/arrière ou un zoom in/out.


Decker_MMIV - fs-uk.com, forum.farming-simulator.com, modhoster.com]]>
        </fr>
    <!-- http://translate.google.com - English to ... - Please PM me a better translation. -->
        <pl>
<![CDATA[Uzyj, aby szybko miec aparat pojazdu;
obrócic 45-stopni w lewo/w prawo, spojrzec do przodu/do tylu lub zoom in/out.


Decker_MMIV - fs-uk.com, forum.farming-simulator.com, modhoster.com]]>
        </pl>
